Package org.logl.log4j2

log4j2 backed logging implementation for logl.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Log4j2Logger
    An implementation of a Logger that delegates logging to a org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger.
    Log4j2LoggerProvider
    An implementation of a LoggerProvider that delegates to org.apache.logging.log4j.LogManager.

Package org.logl.log4j2 Description

log4j2 backed logging implementation for logl.

Classes in this package are available in logl-log4j2.jar, or when including the gradle dependency 'org.logl:logl-log4j2'.
